task.en: Swap Facetime and Contacts in the Dock, keeping other apps at the original position
task.zh: 将Facetime通话和联系人在Dock中的位置对调，保留其它app的位置
task.ar: قم بمبادلة موضع Facetime وجهات الاتصال في الـ Dock، مع الحفاظ على مواقع التطبيقات الأخرى.
task.ja: Dock内でFacetimeと連絡先の位置を交換し、他のアプリの位置は保持してください。
task.ru: Поменяйте местами Facetime и Контакты в Dock, сохранив положения остальных приложений.

grading_command: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to set dockItems to name of every UI element of list 1 of application process "Dock"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "Contacts, Calendar, FaceTime" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to set dockItems to name of every UI element of list 1 of application process "Dock"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "通讯录, 日历, FaceTime通话" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to set dockItems to name of every UI element of list 1 of application process "Dock"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "⁨جهات الاتصال⁩, ‎⁨التقويم⁩, ‎⁨فيس تايم⁩" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to set dockItems to name of every UI element of list 1 of application process "Dock"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "連絡先, カレンダー, FaceTime" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to set dockItems to name of every UI element of list 1 of application process "Dock"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "Контакты, Календарь, FaceTime" && echo "True" || echo "False"
